text: Sofie Svava (born 11 August 2000) is a Danish footballer who plays as a midfielder and has appeared for the Denmark women's national team. ==Career== Svava has been capped for the Denmark national team, appearing for the team during the UEFA Women's Euro 2021 qualifying cycle. ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:2000 births Category:Living people Category:Danish women's footballers Category:Denmark women's international footballers Category:Women's association football midfielders Category:Damallsvenskan players Category:Brøndby IF (women) players Category:FC Rosengård players
